{"tid":1982788,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"（法律jj)求救，關於唔比睇遺囑","createTime":"2020-04-21T11:54:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-21T12:25:46.000Z","uid":94370,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"9dc7f0268973c74771b0c4780b32e6be99f68dc4","tid":1982788,"uid":94370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T11:54:36.000Z","msg":"我有媽媽個家姐岩岩走左<br />\n背景<br />\n生前同老公關係唔太好離家出走左一段時間<br />\n有一個小朋友約十五六歲<br />\n但走之前同一個朋友好fd女人黎大約4，5十歲<br />\n咁佢係走之前12月<br />\n經上術朋友介紹一間律師樓寫遺囑<br />\n就話將全部遺產都比晒果個朋友<br />\n而家我地啲親戚上去律師樓<br />\n佢話冇份分既人冇得睇遺囑。<br />\n連個老公都冇得睇<br />\n請問可以點算<br />\n<br />\n補充女人背景<br />\n但個女人係元朗做生意<br />\n我地一心覺得佢係呃我e媽錢<br />\n借口話拎佢啲錢去幫寵物，但又冇收據<br />\n我e媽病重係醫院果時<br />\n佢擅自上e媽屋企扔晒啲野<br />\n我地聽到o左咀<br />\n人都未走就扔晒啲野<br />\n我地覺得佢身有屎可以點算"},{"pid":"2d9cee0989507caf6da14c9c7e4c1da5adeec887","tid":1982788,"uid":170281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T11:56:57.000Z","msg":"Call消防處"},{"pid":"a9d4d2243642c0c7c3d8f9a466e38af0f9c54521","tid":1982788,"uid":94370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2d9cee0989507caf6da14c9c7e4c1da5adeec887","tid":1982788,"uid":170281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T11:56:57.000Z","msg":"Call消防處"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T11:58:23.000Z","msg":"認真想知點算"},{"pid":"afe09b0f772faa3969f30df0a419864409c1e714","tid":1982788,"uid":287422,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T11:59:54.000Z","msg":"無辦法，最多只能爭議遺囑真確性。<br />\n要先去Probate registry入 Caveat，阻止對方取得遺囑執行書。<br />\n再取法援打官司<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n鬼叫你老母死蠢立遺囑比外人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9058325278d244b4dacc7dc3dab03b33a5f37ccd","tid":1982788,"uid":170281,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a9d4d2243642c0c7c3d8f9a466e38af0f9c54521","tid":1982788,"uid":94370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2d9cee0989507caf6da14c9c7e4c1da5adeec887","tid":198278